Here&#39;s an example policy including the necessary statement.:

    {
       &quot;Version&quot;: &quot;2012-10-17&quot;,
       &quot;Statement&quot;: [{
          &quot;Effect&quot;: &quot;Allow&quot;,
          &quot;Action&quot;: &quot;sqs:GetQueueUrl&quot;,
          &quot;Resource&quot;: &quot;QUEUE_ARN&quot;
       }]
    }

(make sure to replace `QUEUE_ARN` with SQS queue ARN)


