 RSAPrivateCrtKey rsaPrivateKey = (RSAPrivateCrtKey) kf.generatePrivate(keySpecPv);
```

The tips is to use `RSAPrivateCrtKey` class, that expose methode  `rsaPrivateKey.getPublicExponent()`

After that we can call 

```java
